text: Of cymesing on otþunes hyldan ufewyrde andlang ricges oð ða stret niðer andlang strete and swa norð on aggint beorgas of hagging beorgan.
On brynessole of brynessole andlang colredinga ge mercan oð helfesdene oð helfesdene oð lectan æcer, oð lectan æcere, oð wittham ut on ðone feld.
Oð bealdessol of bealdessole, west oð stylfing on ðone kalewanstoce of ðam kalewan stocce on beodune oð ðone ealdanweg andlang weges est ong cymesing.
